  "Description": {
    "English": "Pure Ferrite alloy. Crafted from <span class=\"name name-earth\">Pure Ferrite</span> and <span class=\"name name-earth\">Uranium</span>.<br><br>Used extensively in starship freighter construction due to its sheer strength. A hardcore material popular on the Galactic Trade Network.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "纯铁氧体合金。由<span class=\"name name-earth\">纯铁氧体</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">铀</span>加工而成。<br><br>由于强度很高，广泛应用于货运用星际飞船的建造。银河交易网络中广泛使用的填充材料。",
    "TencentChinese": "纯铁氧体合金。由<span class=\"name name-earth\">纯铁氧体</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">铀</span>加工而成。<br><br>由于强度很高，广泛应用于货运用星际飞船的建造。银河交易网络中广泛使用的填充材料。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "純鐵氧體合金。可使用<span class=\"name name-earth\">純鐵氧體</span>與<span class=\"name name-earth\">鈾</span>製造。<br><br>由於強度驚人，大量應用在太空貨船的建造上。十分剛強的建材，在銀河交易網中十分受歡迎。"
  },
